<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.2">
<l>entai tantai tantai tantaitantaikku</l>
<l>muntai vāṉavar vāṉavar kōṉoṭuñ</l>
<l>cintu pūmaki ḻuntiru vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>tanta milpukaḻ kāreḻi laṇṇalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O the majesty  with raincloud-beauty of endless fame</l>
<l>on Vēṅkaṭam where rejoice in strewing flowers</l>
<l>the former celestials and the king of celestials</l>
<l>to the father of the father of the father of the father of our father.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
